OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776363050
OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,FThe Labour First Minister of Wales has
OL,8,Fcalled for the UK Government to stop
OL,9,Fwork on a defence project with the US.
OL,11,FEluned Morgan said the United States
OL,12,Fis "not the partner it once was" and
OL,13,Furged the UK Government to halt
OL,14,Finvolvement in the Deep Space Advanced
OL,15,FRadar Capability (Darc) programme.
OL,17,FThe Cawdor Barracks in Pembrokeshire
OL,18,Fis expected to house the main UK
OL,19,Fcontribution to the project, alongside
OL,20,Fsites in the US and Australia.
OL,26,@tD@DOUtD@`O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776363050
OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,FEluned Morgan said, "I'm calling for
OL,8,Fthe Darc defence project in
OL,9,FPembrokeshire to be halted.
OL,11,F"The United States under Donald Trump
OL,12,Fis not the partner it once was.
OL,14,F"Talk of targeting civilians,
OL,15,Fundermining our allies, and
OL,16,Fdiminishing the sacrifice of our armed
OL,17,Fforces is not the conduct of a
OL,18,Freliable ally.
OL,26,@oD@UOUsD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776363050
OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,F"I believe in international alliances,
OL,8,FI believe in collective security, but
OL,9,Fthere is a clear difference between
OL,10,Fstanding with our partners and giving
OL,11,Fa free pass to a US president who has
OL,12,Fthreatened war crimes and shown
OL,13,Fcontempt for our country.
OL,15,F"I'm urging the UK Government to halt
OL,16,Four involvement in the Aukus radar
OL,17,Fproject until we can be confident
OL,18,Fthose partnerships reflect our values,
OL,19,Fand our security interests."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776363050
OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,FThe Darc programme will see a network
OL,8,Fof radars developed in Australia and
OL,9,Fthe US, as well as the UK, to provide
OL,10,Fglobal monitoring of the skies,
OL,11,Fincreasing the Aukus nations' ability
OL,12,Fto track objects in space.
OL,14,FThe use of three sites is expected to
OL,15,Fprovide coverage of the sky at all
OL,16,Ftimes of day and under any weather
OL,17,Fconditions, and the UK's contribution
OL,18,Fto this project is described as
OL,19,F"crucial to its success".
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776363050
OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer's political spokesman
OL,8,Fdeclined to say whether the Prime
OL,9,FMinister backed the First Minister's
OL,10,Fcomments but appeared to distance
OL,11,FDowning Street from the suggestion
OL,12,Fthat work should pause.
OL,14,FHe said, "The Deep Space Advanced
OL,15,FRadar Capability programme will secure
OL,16,Flong-term jobs in Pembrokeshire, Wales
OL,17,Fand help protect essential satellite
OL,18,Fcommunication and navigation works.
OL,26,@vD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776363050
OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,F"We're engaging with the local
OL,8,Fcommunity on proposals to redevelop
OL,9,FCawdor Barracks to host Darc, which
OL,10,Fwill be operated by UK personnel.
OL,12,F"We are following processes agreed
OL,13,Fwith Pembrokeshire County Council and
OL,14,Fhave already completed a comprehensive
OL,15,Fenvironmental impact assessment to
OL,16,Fensure the project has minimal impact
OL,17,Fon the local skyline.
OL,19,F"Cawdor Barracks has a long history of
OL,20,Fsupporting the UK's military.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
