OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,F"This site has been both a Royal Air
OL,8,FForce flying station and a Royal Navy
OL,9,Fbase."
OL,11,FA Ministry of Defence Spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid, "The Deep Space Advanced Radar
OL,13,FCapability (DARC) programme will
OL,14,Fsecure long-term jobs in
OL,15,FPembrokeshire, Wales and help protect
OL,16,Fessential satellite communication and
OL,17,Fnavigation networks.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@FO]tD@GOU
