OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776363050
OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,FA Reform spokesperson said, "It's
OL,8,Fclear that Eluned Morgan is focusing
OL,9,Fon non-devolved issues to distract
OL,10,Ffrom her party's appalling record in
OL,11,FGovernment with Plaid Cymru."
OL,13,FA Plaid Cymru spokesperson said, "This
OL,14,Fis nothing but a last-ditch attempt by
OL,15,FEluned Morgan to cling on to her seat.
OL,17,F"Since becoming First Minister, she
OL,18,Fhas chosen to stay quiet on defence
OL,19,Fand international affairs, only now
OL,20,Fspeaking up after polls show her
OL,21,Flosing her seat."
OL,26,@uD@bOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
