OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776363050
OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,FCommenting, Leader of the Welsh
OL,8,FConservatives, Darren Millar said,
OL,9,F"Let's be absolutely clear - we are
OL,10,Fliving in a dangerously unstable
OL,11,Fworld, with growing threats from
OL,12,Fcountries like Russia and Iran.
OL,14,F"At a time like this, it is
OL,15,Fextraordinary that Eluned Morgan is
OL,16,Fwilling to put our national security
OL,17,Fat risk.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
