PN,46611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776363050
OL,3,CWelsh Labour First Minister calls for
OL,4,Chalt to involvement in US defence
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,FA Welsh Liberal Democrat Spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid, "Donald Trump has made it clear
OL,9,Fhe sees Europe as a problem, not a
OL,10,Fpartner - and that poses serious
OL,11,Fthreats for the AUKUS programme.
OL,13,F"We need an urgent review of the risks
OL,14,Fthat Trump might pull out of the
OL,15,Fprogramme - as well as what is needed
OL,16,Fto mitigate the potential consequences
OL,17,Ffor the UK's and Australia's defences."
OL,19,FThe Green Party have been approached
OL,20,Ffor comment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/12
